<h2 class="bold font-l">The Mafia Attack Sting</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Sting is betrayed by the Main Event Mafia. He attempts to get payback with his trademark baseball bat, but the attempt backfires. </p>
